==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''docket'''

# a [[schedule]] of [[case]]s awaiting [[action]] in a [[court]]
# a short entry of the [[proceeding]]s of a court; the [[register]] containing them; the [[office]] containing the register
# an [[agenda]] of things to be done
# a [[ticket]] or [[label]] fixed to something, showing its [[content]]s or directions to its [[use]]

===Transitive verb===
'''to docket'''
# to make an entry in a docket
# to [[label]] a [[parcel]] etc